# GRAPHICS::USE_SNOW_FOOT_VFX_WHEN_UNSHELTERED

## Summary
When the ped is unsheltered all foot effects will use the snow vfx group

## Parameters
* **BOOL** enable

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Forces footstep tracks on all surfaces.
